{"tid":701440,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"［老鏡］大家對90mm Macro鏡有咩睇法？","createTime":"2018-06-14T06:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T17:21:19.000Z","uid":81908,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3848e3651d6d5b48572ebb1bf718700c9b25b3","tid":701440,"uid":81908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"我見啲老鏡post都沉曬，唯有自己開個post聽下大家意見。<br />\n<br />\n講下我用咩機先，咁我就用菲林機om-1(n)（器材撚、數碼撚勿屌）。<br />\n<br />\n最近用日本Yahoo 2.9k+運費bid咗支om 90mm f/2 Macro玩下。因為我見平時啲人吹到話孔雀翎、七武器，咁個價又平市面一半，就試下bid，又真係俾我bid到。<br />\n<br />\n入返正題，我平時影開人像為主，或者濕鳩街拍，不過其實都係玩咗半年到，好新嘅新手。我想請教下，90mm鏡應該點樣構圖，點樣玩？其實啱唔啱影人像？因為呢支始終都係Macro鏡，影花草蟲係唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無師兄分享下經驗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/143525_fb0e10229ec48374e3a9e82cfd237d2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F143525_fb0e10229ec48374e3a9e82cfd237d2a.png&h=6a11967a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"694ec20ce54653926d64e24e0ce0891d2a6c9a84","tid":701440,"uid":4806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"留名學野，岩岩買左支contax g90"},{"pid":"742820c9e7de6da1d2647977d4aeef413e75f8c2","tid":701440,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"有支272E 路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307c60cdaa21f4a2c8a757361db44f21467f7863","tid":701440,"uid":114518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"攞嚟影人其實冇問題㗎<br />\n我覺得Macro鏡係擴闊咗個範圍去Macro啫<br />\n照樣當普通定焦都一樣好用"},{"pid":"8b51b77e13cdcc5e24dc173de4e4c9c396a8e81f","tid":701440,"uid":81908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:40:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c199af89bcd9f7d368b091da37637112ce9e382a","tid":70144